About Pinecrest Mobile Home Park
​
Have you ever wanted to own your own vacation home?  Our community may be just the place
you're looking for!
With our low maintenance and lot rental fees, (includes water,
garbage, sewer and lawn care), we just might convince you to make this your home away from
home or maybe your only home!
​
Pinecrest Mobile Home Park is a 55+ community and we are located in the charming little city of
Zephyrhills, Florida, which is located between the two large cities of Tampa and Orlando.
At Pinecrest you'll get the small town atmosphere, that many people love, without giving up access to top amenities-- like local shopping centers, flea markets, or top quality health
care and emergency services.
​
For beach goers, one of the best in the United States is an easy drive away on the Gulf Coast.
Fishing charters, dinner cruises, an evening at the Hard Rock Casino, a day visiting exotic wildlife
at Bush Gardens, or a trip to see the Manatees in Crystal River- are all within about an hour, or two hour drive.
You'll find plenty to do either in the community or as a day trip.​​
​
Our clubhouse,  is a central hub for those that like to play cards or games and/or
billiards. We typically have monthly potluck dinners and many social
activities; which allows us to get to know our neighbors better.
​
​
​
​
​
​
